headline: Steelcase (SCS) Tops Q2 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
summary: Steelcase (SCS) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +21.62% and +2.58%, respectively, for the quarter ended August 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
